Shop RHW is a Toronto-based studio with a focus on solid wood custom furniture hand crafted by Rundell Haynes-Wells. 
In addition to being a craftsman, he also offers custom design consultation and renderings.

Rundell combines years of experience problem solving, exploring, and innovating, and has been a maker of things all of his life. 
He’s a natural born collaborator and is generous with the information he shares with his clients in the hope that more knowledge and understanding of custom furniture will inspire sustained interest and appreciation.

Please give me a call - 647-453-0093

The Chesterfield Shop...Your Leather and Fabric Superstore & More!
Since 1948, this family owned and operated chain of Leather, Fabric and Home Theatre seating superstores, has been prouding serving generations of satisfied customers who keep coming back again and again for the great selection, quality, service and value..
You'll find an ocean of contemporary, stylish and colourful sofas, sofabeds (w/great mattresses for the most comfortable sleep), loveseats, chairs, sectionals, home theatre, recliners with power, ottomans with storage PLUS thousands of outstanding furnishing accessories like coffee and end tables, lamps, carpets, wall art & more.
With five convenient locations to serve you in the Toronto GTA and Newmarket. 
Huge Inventory, Special Orders, Leathers To Go Express™ Next Day Delivery on many stocked items, and even Delivery to Cottage Country!

Home Proud and Money Wise?  Come to The Chesterfield Shop.

 OUR LOW PRICES LIVE ALL YEAR ROUND.


Urban Accents is a family owned business which has been in the furniture industry for the past 12 years, constantly striving to make our customers shopping experience satisfying and enjoyable. 

***

By keep our overhead and management cost low, we pass on the savings to our customers by keeping our prices close to wholesale prices.
Because of our extensive experience in this business, we bring the latest designs and trends and constantly getting in new products to cater to a wide variety of clientele.
We hope to see you soon, and appreciate all our previous customers for their business.

profile:
IS ASSEMBLY
A FRUSTRATING?
WASTE OF YOUR TIME?
NO WORRIES! 
CALL US NOW : 647-8825454
______________________________________________

We offer the IKEA Pickup, delivery and assembly service.

We normally need a few days in advance for bookings, but if you have an urgent need, just let us know.

Sometimes we can send a team right away to your location.

We have experienced professionals who are knowledgeable and skilled when it comes to putting together all that IKEA furniture you love to order and can't wait to get set up in your home!

We do it all, whether it is a bed, bookcase or shelving system; our assemblers can do it with ease and have your piece put together and installed in your home where you want it.

Our prices are very reasonable and fair for similar services in the Greater Toronto Area.

Please check our site:
http://leonexpress.ca/assembly/
